The markets latest rally attempt which began on 51419 rolled over and died last week So once again we find ourselves waiting for the COMPQ or SPX to begin to rally and ultimately followthrough which would indicate that a new uptrend may be underway For this to happen either index must rise at least 17 on more volume than the day before Ideally a followthrough day should occur on days 47 of a rally attempt although a valid followthrough day can still show up weeks laterSurprisingly quite a few of the markets high growth leaders have held up extremely well despite the recent weakness in the general market Remember a broad base of healthy leadership is critical to the sustainability of a new uptrend So its a big positive to see high quality names from the technology and medicalhealthcare sectors exhibiting strength and resilience while the general market is in correction mode QQQ IWM DIAtraderlioncomtop10reporShow More
